Package annotation.calcs.snr

Class SNRAnnotationType

java.lang.Object
annotation.DataAnnotationType<SNRAnnotation>
annotation.calcs.snr.SNRAnnotationType
public class SNRAnnotationType extends DataAnnotationType<SNRAnnotation>
SNR annotation type. Can add a single double SNR to a data unit. Can automatically calculate the SNR from the time frequency box of the data unit.
Author:
Doug Gillespie
